                            <comment id="13258857" author="yseeley@gmail.com" created="Sat, 21 Apr 2012 13:59:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You can see this by executing the following update command, and observing another commit 15 seconds later (caused by autocommit)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;curl http:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//localhost:8983/solr/update/json?commit=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;Content-type:application/json&apos;&lt;/span&gt; -d &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;[{&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;id&quot;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;2&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;foo_t&quot;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;x y&quot;&lt;/span&gt;}]&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13258862" author="yseeley@gmail.com" created="Sat, 21 Apr 2012 14:25:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Well.... this would explain it &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/wink.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/** Inform tracker that a commit has occurred */&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void didCommit() {
  }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
